ously)"},{"type":"text","text":"[smart]"},{"type":"text","text":"图be smitten with/by sb./sth.突然爱上，完全迷上"},{"type":"entry","text":"stubby","headword":"stubby"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 短粗的(being short and thickset)"},{"type":"text","text":"['stAbi]"},{"type":"text","text":"squat, stocky, stumpy"},{"type":"entry","text":"sock","headword":"sock"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.重击，痛打（to strike forcefully)"},{"type":"text","text":"[sa:k]"},{"type":"text","text":"sock更广为人知的意思是“短袜”"},{"type":"entry","text":"unthreatening","headword":"unthreatening"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad不危险的"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'θretnrn]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：un（不）+threatening（危险的）→不危险的"}]},{"number":440,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 41 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"rebuttal","headword":"rebuttal"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.反驳，反证(argument or proof that rebuts)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'bAtl]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：re（反）+butt顶撞）+al→反过来顶撞→反驳"},{"type":"entry","text":"divagate","headword":"divagate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 离题(to stray from the subject);漂泊(to wander about)"},{"type":"text","text":"['darvagert]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：di（离开）+vag（漫游）+ate→（思想）漫游→离题"},{"type":"entry","text":"waspish","headword":"waspish"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 易怒的(irascible, petulant, snappish);尖刻的"},{"type":"text","text":"[wa:spr]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自wasp（n.黄蜂）"},{"type":"entry","text":"snooze","headword":"snooze"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.打盹儿，打睦睡(to take a nap)"},{"type":"text","text":"[snu:z]"},{"type":"text","text":"catnap, doze, siesta"},{"type":"entry","text":"felicitate","headword":"felicitate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 祝贺，庆祝(to wish happiness to; congratulate)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fa'lrsrtert]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：felic（幸福）+itate→使-幸福→祝贺"},{"type":"entry","text":"well-groomed","headword":"well-groomed"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj整齐干净的，衣着入时的"},{"type":"text","text":"[wel'gru:md]"},{"type":"text",