n illicit love affair)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ll'erza:n]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：lia（捆）+ison→捆在一起→密切的联系"},{"type":"entry","text":"phoenix","headword":"phoenix"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 凤凰, 长生鸟(an imaginary bird believed to live for 500 years and then burn"},{"type":"text","text":"['f:nrks]"},{"type":"text","text":"itself and be born again from the ashes)"},{"type":"entry","text":"glare","headword":"glare"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 发炫光(to shine with dazzling light);怒目而视(to stare fiercely or angrily)"},{"type":"text","text":"[gler]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：和flare（n./v闪光）一起记"},{"type":"entry","text":"deduct","headword":"deduct"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.减去，扣除(to take away an amount or a part)：演绎(to deduce)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'dakt]"},{"type":"text","text":"abate, discount, rebate, subtract"},{"type":"entry","text":"antecedence","headword":"antecedence"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.居先，先行（priority.precedence)"},{"type":"text","text":"[aentr'si:dns]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ante（前面）+ced（走）+ence→走在前面→居先，先行"},{"type":"entry","text":"inexpedient","headword":"inexpedient"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.不适当的，不明智的(inadvisable, unwise)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rnik'spi:diant]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：in（不）+expedient（有利的）→不利的→不明智的"},{"type":"text","text":"groom"},{"type":"entry","text":"groom","headword":"groom"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.马夫：新郎（bridegroom）"},{"type":"text","text":"[gru:m]"},{"type":"text","text":"圈联想记忆：g（谐音“哥”）+room（房间）→哥进房间接自"},{"type":"text","text":"己的新娘→新郎"},{"type":"entry","text":"apostate","headword":"apostate"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.背教者：变节者（a person guilty of apostasy)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'pa:stert]"},{"type":"text","text":"flopper, renegade, turnabout, turncoat"},{"type":"entry","text":"strangulation","headword":"strangulation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 拒杀，勒死(the action or process of strangling or strangulating)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,straengju'lex{n]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自strangle（v扼杀，抑制)"},{"type":"entry","text":"medicate","headword":"medicate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 用药物医治(to treat with medicine)"},{"type":"text","text":"['medikert]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：medic（治疗）+ate→用药物医治"},{"type":"entry","text":"innuendo","headword":"innuendo"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.含沙射影，哈讽(an indirect remark, gesture, or reference, usually implying sth."},{"type":"text","text":"[rnju'endau]"},{"type":"text","text":"derogatory; insinuation)"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：in（向）+nuen（摇头）+do→向某人摇头→暗讽"},{"type":"text","text":"Demonstrating a mastery of innuenclo, he issued several veiled insults in the"},{"type":"text","text":"course of the evening's conversation."},{"type":"entry","text":"delinquent","headword":"delinquent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 怠忽职守的(failing or neglecting to do what duty or law requires)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'lrnkwant]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：de（离开）+linqu（离开）+ent→一再离开（正道）的→怠忽职守的"},{"type":"entry","text":"desideratum","headword":"desideratum"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 必需品(sth. needed and wanted)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：desider（看作desire，渴望）+atum→渴望的东西→必需品"},{"type":"text","text":"[d1,zida'rertam]"},{"type":"entry","text":"announce","headword":"announce"},{"type":"definition","text":"v宣布，发表（to proclaim)：通报的到来（to give notice of the arrival)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'nauns]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：an（加强）+nounc（说）+e→讲出来→宣布"},{"type":"entry","text":"petulance","headword":"petulance"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.易怒，性急，暴躁（the quality or state of being petulant)"},{"type":"text","text":"['petfalans]"},{"type":"entry","text":"peevishness","headword":"peevishness"},{"type":"entry","text":"daze","headword":"daze"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.迷乱，恍愧v.使范然，使眩晕(to stun as with a blow or shock; benumb)"},{"type":"text","text":"[derz]"},{"type":"text","text":"in a daze 迷茫"},{"type":"entry","text":"unfold","headword":"unfold"},{"type":"definition","text":"v展开，打开（to open from a folded position）：逐渐呈现"}]},{"number":443,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"For those who admire realism, Louis Malle's recent film succeeds because"},{"type":"text","text":"it consciously shuns the stuff of legend and tells an unembellished story as it"},{"type":"text","text":"might actually unfoic with flible people in earthly time."},{"type":"entry","text":"snitch","headword":"snitch"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 告密(to tell about the wrongdoings of a friend); f(to steal by taking quickly)"},{"type":"text","text":"[snrt]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：sni（看作sin，罪行）+tch→告密和偷都是罪行→告密；偷"},{"type":"entry","text":"complaisant","headword":"complaisant"},{"type":"text","text":"adfj.顺从的：讨好的(affably agreeable; obliging)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kam'pleizant]"},{"type":"text","text":"accommodating. indulgent"},{"type":"entry","text":"buffer","headword":"buffer"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 缓冲,减轻(to lessen the effect of a blow or collision)"},{"type":"text","text":"['bAfar]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：buff（软皮）+er→缓冲"},{"type":"entry","text":"parlous","headword":"parlous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj靠不住的，危险的(full of danger;hazardous)"},{"type":"text","text":"['pa:rlas]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：和perilous（acj危险的）一起记"},{"type":"entry","text":"smooth","headword":"smooth"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使平坦，使光滑（to make smooth)：消除adj光滑的：平稳的"},{"type":"text","text":"In response to the follies of todiay's commercial and political worlds, the"},{"type":"text","text":"[smu:0]"},{"type":"text","text":"author does not express inflamed indignation, but rather affects the detachment"},{"type":"text","text":"and smooth aphoristic prose of an eighteenth-century wit."},{"type":"entry","text":"underbid","headword":"underbid"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.叫价低于：要价过低（to bid toolow)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Andar'brd]"},{"type":"text","text":"图组合词：under（低于）+bid（出价）→叫价低于"},{"type":"entry","text":"donate","headword":"donate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.捐赠，赠送(to give money, goods to a charity)"},{"type":"text","text":"['daunert]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：don（给予）+ate→捐赠，赠送"},{"type":"entry","text":"poke","headword":"poke"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 刺，截(to prod; stab; thrust)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pauk]"},{"type":"text","text":"poke fun at 嘲弄，戏弄"},{"type":"entry","text":"unprovoked","headword":"unprovoked"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.无缘无故的(not caused by previous action)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Anpra'vaukt]"},{"type":"entry","text":"repent","headword":"repent"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 便悔，后梅(to feel regret or contrition)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'pent]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：re（重新）+pent（惩罚）→心灵再次受到惩罚→快悔"},{"type":"entry","text":"growl","headword":"growl"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. (动物）咆哮，吼叫(to make a low, rumbling,menacing sound);(雷电等)轰鸣"},{"type":"text","text":"[graul]"},{"type":"text","text":"国联想记忆：gr+owl（猫头鹰）→猫头鹰叫→跑哮，吼叫"},{"type":"entry","text":"debility","headword":"debility"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.衰弱，虚弱(weakness or feebleness)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'brlati]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：de（去掉）+bility（看作ability，能力）→失去能力→衰弱"},{"type":"entry","text":"dissociate","headword":"dissociate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 分离，游离，分裂(to separate from association or union with another)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'saufiert]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：dis（不）+soci（同伴；社会）+ate→不成为伙伴的→分离，游离"},{"type":"entry","text":"intersperse","headword":"intersperse"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.散布，点级(to place sth. at intervals in or among)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Intar'sps:rs]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：inter（在…之间）+spers（散开）+e→散开在之间→点缀"}]},{"number":444,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 41 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"recusant","headword":"recusant"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 拒绝服从的人(one who refuses to accept or obey established authority)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ra'kju:zant]"},{"type":"entry","text":"fragrance","headword":"fragrance"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.香料;香味(pleasant or sweet smell)"},{"type":"text","text":"['frergrans]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自fragrant（adj芳香的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"vertex","headword":"vertex"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.（三角形等的）顶角：顶点，最高点（summit;the highest point)"},{"type":"text","text":"['v3:rteks]"},{"type":"text","text":"apex, crest, crown, height"},{"type":"entry","text":"effeminate","headword":"effeminate"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 缺乏勇气的，柔弱的(having the qualities generally attributed to women)"},{"type":"text","text":"[x'feminat]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：ef（出）+femin（女）+ate→露出女人气→柔弱的"},{"type":"entry","text":"revulsion","headword":"revulsion"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 厌恶，增恶(a sense of utter distaste);剧变(a sudden or strong reaction)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'val§n]"},{"type":"entry","text":"disport","headword":"disport"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.玩要，嬉戏（to indulge in amusement)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'sp>:rt]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：dis（加强）+port（带）→带走（时间）→玩耍"},{"type":"entry","text":"rasp","headword":"rasp"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.发出刺耳的声音（to make a harsh noise)：锉，刮削"},{"type":"text","text":"[raesp]"},{"type":"text","text":"rasp sth.away/off 锉掉某物"},{"type":"entry","text":"fondle","headword":"fondle"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 抚弄，抚接(to stroke or handle in a tender and loving way; caress)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fa:nd]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自fond（adj喜爱的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"outshine","headword":"outshine"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.比-光亮（to shine brighter than）;出色，优异（to excel in splendor or"},{"type":"text","text":"[aut'farn]"},{"type":"text","text":"showiness)"},{"type":"text","text":"组合词：out(超越）+shine(闪耀）→出色"},{"type":"entry","text":"latch","headword":"latch"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.门门v用门门门牢"},{"type":"text","text":"[lat]"},{"type":"text","text":"固联想记忆：和catch（v.抓住）一起记"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 狂欢(an unrestrained indulgence in or outburst of an activity)"},{"type":"entry","text":"jagged","headword":"jagged"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.锯齿状的，参差不齐的（notched orragged）"},{"type":"text","text":"['d3aegid]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自jag（v使成锯齿状）"},{"type":"entry","text":"slander","headword":"slander"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.谦谤，诞毁（todefame)n.谦谤，中伤"},{"type":"text","text":"['slaendar]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：s+land（地）+er→把人贬到地上→谁谤，证毁"},{"type":"entry","text":"premiere","headword":"premiere"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.（电影、戏剧等）首次公演（a first performance or exhibition）"},{"type":"text","text":"[prr'mrr]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自premier（adj.首要的；最早的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"destitution","headword":"destitution"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.缺乏，穷困(the state of being destitute)"},{"type":"text","text":"[destr'tu:{n]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自destitute（adj贫困的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"potation","headword":"potation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 喝，饮(the act of drinking or inhaling); 饮料,酒(an alcoholic drink)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pau'ter{n]"}]},{"number":445,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"plaza","headword":"plaza"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 广场(a public square); 集市(shopping center)"},{"type":"text","text":"['plaeza]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自拉丁语platea，意为“庭院；宽散的大街”"},{"type":"entry","text":"acrobat","headword":"acrobat"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.特技演员，杂技演员（one that performs gymnastic feats requiring skilful"},{"type":"text","text":"['ekrabaet]"},{"type":"text","text":"control of the body)"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：acro（高）+bat（走）→高空走的人→杂技演员"},{"type":"entry","text":"pinch","headword":"pinch"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.捏，拍（to compress; squeeze) n. —握，少量（a very small amount)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pint"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：p+inch（英寸）→以英寸计量的→一报"},{"type":"entry","text":"wizened","headword":"wizened"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 干枯的，干德的，干皱的(dry, shrunken, and wrinkled as a result of aging or"},{"type":"text","text":"['wiznd]"},{"type":"text","text":"of faling vitality)"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自wizen（v起皱，干德）"},{"type":"entry","text":"pervert","headword":"pervert"},{"type":"definition","text":"v使重落(to comupt;debase);温用(to divert to a wrong purpose;misuse)：歪曲"},{"type":"text","text":"[par'v3:rt]"},{"type":"text","text":"(to interpret incorrectly)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：per（远离）+vert（转）→越转越远离正途→使重落"},{"type":"entry","text":"nethermost","headword":"nethermost"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 最低的，最下面的(lowest; the farthest down)"},{"type":"text","text":"['nedamaust]"},{"type":"text","text":"园组合词：nether（下面的）+most（最）→最下面的"},{"type":"entry","text":"slink","headword":"slink"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 淄走，潜逃(to go or move stealthily or furtively)"},{"type":"text","text":"[slink]"},{"type":"text","text":"creep"},{"type":"entry","text":"burial","headword":"burial"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 埋葬，埋藏(the act or ceremony of putting a dead body into a grave)"},{"type":"text","text":"来自bury（v.埋葬，掩埋）"},{"type":"text","text":"['berial]"},{"type":"entry","text":"mnemonics","headword":"mnemonics"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 记忆法, 记t忆术(the technique of developing the memory)"},{"type":"text","text":"[nr'ma:niks]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：mne（记忆)+mon+ics→记忆法"},{"type":"entry","text":"entourage","headword":"entourage"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 随从(group of attendants; retinue); 环境(surroundings)"},{"type":"text","text":"['a:ntura:3]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：en+tour（旅行）+age（年龄）→上了年龄旅行必须有随从→随从"},{"type":"entry","text":"ultramundane","headword":"ultramundane"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj世界之外的：超俗的"},{"type":"text","text":"[Altra'mandein]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：ultra(超出）+mund（世界）+ane→超俗的"},{"type":"entry","text":"pendent","headword":"pendent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.吊着的，悬挂的（overhanging)"},{"type":"text","text":"['pendant]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：pend（挂）+ent→挂着的→吊着的，悬挂的"},{"type":"text","text":"vegetate"},{"type":"entry","text":"vegetate","headword":"vegetate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.像植物那样生长(to grow in the manner of a plant)：无"},{"type":"text","text":"['vedzatert]"},{"type":"text","text":"所事事地生活（to lead a passive existence without"},{"type":"text","text":"exertion of body or mind)"},{"type":"text","text":"不找工作"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：和vegetable（n.蔬菜）一起记"},{"type":"text","text":"无所事事"},{"type":"entry","text":"emolument","headword":"emolument"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 报酬，新水(remuneration)"},{"type":"text","text":"[r'ma:ljumant]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：e（向外）+molu（碾碎）+ment→磨坊主加工粮食后所得的钱→报酬"},{"type":"entry","text":"subcelestial","headword":"subcelestial"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.世俗的，尘世的(worldly)"}]},{"number":446,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 41 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"fatidic","headword":"fatidic"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj. 预言的(of or relating to prophecy)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fae'tidrk]"},{"type":"entry","text":"exclamation","headword":"exclamation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.惊叹词：惊呼(a sharp or sudden utterance)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ex（出）+clam（叫，喊）+ation→大声喊出来→惊呼"},{"type":"text","text":"[ekskla'mer[n]"},{"type":"entry","text":"jumpy","headword":"jumpy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj紧张不安的，心惊肉跳的（onedge;nervous)"},{"type":"text","text":"['d3Ampi]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自jump（v.跳：惊跳）"},{"type":"entry","text":"easel","headword":"easel"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 黑板架,画架(wooden frame for holding a blackboard or a picture)"},{"type":"text","text":"[i:zl]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：ease（轻松）+l→有了画架，画起画来轻松多了→画架"},{"type":"entry","text":"floppy","headword":"floppy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 松软的(soft and flexible);软弱的(flabby. fiaccid)"},{"type":"text","text":"['fla:pi]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：f+loppy（下垂的）→松软的"}]}]}